Lunarpine still didn't like the monster before him. The freak of nature was
the ugliest thing he'd seen since he'd landed. "You still haven't said why
you're here." he says stating the obvious.

Megaton waved off the wolf like he didn't exist. "I must be going, I have
business at your base." he turned his back and added "I'm sorry, I meant the
Maximals base." He spread his wings again and flew toward the Cybertronian
fires scanning range.

Lunarpine transformed to wolf mode and started chaseing the mutant. He
opened his mind to Ice, knowing any comm would be intercepted by the monster
above.

"Ice, if you can hear me, warn the Maximals that something big and ugly with
big sharp teeth is flying that way." He thought, hoping that he was in her
range.
